VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.innerHTML\s?=\s?.+
WHEN EXPR MISSING:DOMPurify\.sanitize|sanitizeHtml|textContent|innerText|escapeHtml|encodeHTML && MISSING:test|example|spec
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential security risks when assigning untrusted data to the innerHTML property.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Data in InnerHTML.
